al_techsallus_about_01													I started my career as an apprentice, performing the role of report development within the TechSallus system.
al_techsallus_about_02													I was responsible for the development, maintenance, and enhancement of the TechSallus system. I played a key role in developing the endoscopy video system within the clinic module, as well as in managing the occupational health module. Additionally, I am actively involved in web development for TechSallus using ASP.NET MVC technology. My goal is to ensure that the system operates efficiently, providing an enhanced user experience and meeting the specific demands of the healthcare sector.
